    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-10-17T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-10-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="461" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d461">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Señor
                                    <persName type="to">Romero</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-10-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 17,
                                    1893</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge the
                            receipt of your note of the 13th instant further relating to the pursuit
                            of marauders on June 30 last by Texas Rangers across the boundary line
                            into Mexico, and to say that I have made known its contents to the
                            governor of Texas. Accept, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Alvey A. Adee</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
